  "instructions": [
    "Cut the potatoes into thin strips and soak them in cold water for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Drain the potatoes and pat them dry with a paper towel.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the potatoes to the skillet and cook for 3-4 minutes on each side, or until they are golden brown.",
    "Add the garlic, salt, black pepper, turmeric, cumin, and paprika to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, or until the potatoes are coated in the spice mixture.",
    "Remove the skillet from the heat and stir in the lemon juice.",
    "Transfer the fries to a serving dish and sprinkle with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
